BMW Car Sales Analysis Dashboard (2010–2024)

An interactive Power BI dashboard analyzing BMW global sales trends, revenue performance, and fuel-type insights from 2010 to 2024.
Project Overview

This project explores BMW’s worldwide sales using a combination of revenue, price, mileage, and model data. The dashboard provides insights into:

1. Sales volume trends across 2010–2024

2. Revenue by region and by model

3. Performance differences across fuel types

4. KPIs for identifying high-performing markets

5. Storytelling insights created for business decision-makers

Goal: The goal is to simulate a real business analytics scenario, showing how data can drive decisions on market strategy, pricing, and car model focus.
